# Frontend Angular (CLI 19)

- **Stack:** Angular CLI 19 standalone components, routing, Karma/Jasmine tests.
- UI is metadata-driven: dynamic forms and universal grid only — no entity-specific field components.
- Entity UX: `src/app/pages/entity/entity-list.component.ts` + `entity-record.component.ts` (separate list/record routes — **A15**).
- Shell: `src/app/pages/shell/shell.component.ts` + child routes in `app.routes.ts`.
- API: `EmcapApiService` → `api/emcap-client.ts` (Bearer + `X-Tenant-ID`).
- Metadata: `src/app/metadata/contract.ts` + `dynamic-form.renderer.ts` / `dynamic-grid.renderer.ts`.
- CI: `npm run build` + `npm run test:ci` (ChromeHeadless).
- Archived Vite shell: `clients/web-legacy/` — do not edit.

## TypeScript

`tsconfig.json` sets `noPropertyAccessFromIndexSignature: false` for API `Record<string, unknown>` payloads.

## Scaffold new components

```bash
cd clients/web
ng generate component pages/my-feature --standalone
```
